# (also '''bunnyhug''', '''bunny-hug''') According to the [[w:Canadian Oxford Dictionary|Canadian Oxford Dictionary]], a hooded [[sweater]] in some parts of [[Canada]], specifically [[Saskatchewan]].  Bunny-hugs generally have a single large pocket across the front, at waist level, with an opening on both the left and right sides.

